    Black Aracnia looked deep into his optics, "Dont worry. Megatron and Hell 
Beast are on Kitkats leash. They wont do anything, besides, we control the 
bulk of the troops. They wont do---by the Matrix!" She cried.
    Suddenly Aracnia grabbed her stomach, it was time. Finally, labor had set 
in and she could feel the small Predacon inside fighting its way out into the 
Beasts Wars.
    "Quickstrike, I think im having the baby!"
